WEBVTT

00:00:28.399 --> 00:00:30.495
yet 40 percent of board directors

00:00:30.519 --> 00:00:32.954
don't think climate belongs
in the boardroom.

00:00:33.704 --> 00:00:36.284
And we have kids marching
in the streets now,

00:00:36.308 --> 00:00:39.333
asking us to be accountable
for their future.

00:00:39.822 --> 00:00:41.982
We have a crisis of inequality.

00:00:42.006 --> 00:00:44.713
We have Yellow Jackets
not just in the streets of France,

00:00:44.737 --> 00:00:46.180
but all over the world,

00:00:46.204 --> 00:00:48.363
and yet we continue to see examples

00:00:48.387 --> 00:00:52.433
of businesses and other leaders
fueling that anger.

00:00:52.923 --> 00:00:54.968
BF: Do you think
the pitchforks are coming?

00:00:54.992 --> 00:00:57.258
HT: I definitely think
this is not sustainable.

00:00:57.282 --> 00:00:59.527
And the reason why it's so difficult

00:00:59.551 --> 00:01:03.898
for us to deal with these complicated
crises that are interrelated